{"tid":2095044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年前，和理非：唔走搏拉咩！ 勇武派：咁細膽點贏呀！","createTime":"2020-07-05T07:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T14:13:00.000Z","uid":267881,"like":27,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fe309041c3ed7ac6b7d5ca6e40bd669f0d5c2313","tid":2095044,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"2019年，每次遊行集會都會在街頭上演呢個戲碼，互相指責，互相質疑<br />\n<br />\n和理非：邊個叫人衝邊個就係鬼<br />\n勇武派：邊個叫人走邊個就係鬼<br />\n<br />\n和理非：留咁夜為咩姐<br />\n勇武派：你班冷氣軍師冇資格指指點點<br />\n<br />\n和理非：點解你地唔肯用腦，咁硬頸？<br />\n勇武派：點解你地咁自私，走精面？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到2020年，本質冇變，即係冇進步過<br />\n<br />\n和理非：留喺香港等入集中營咩<br />\n勇武派：邊個叫人移民邊個就係鬼<br />\n<br />\n和理非：拎走D錢咪仲有助抗爭<br />\n勇武派：你地走咗仲邊會參與抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一路走來，始終如一：分化<br />\n甚麼不足鬼不分化不割蓆be water呢？<br />\n<br />\n又話五毛分別扮演最理性嘅和理非同最激進嘅勇武派<br />\n<br />\n咁快唔記得過去一年係點樣和勇不分互相尊重？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在、未來<br />\n留港 = 前綫 = 勇武派<br />\n移民 = 後勤 = 和理非<br />\n<br />\n呢個係大勢所趨，不能逆轉<br />\n你哋識玩嘅"},{"pid":"c6d2bdd9cf161f2bd9cbdbc43ef28d77c900eb4e","tid":2095044,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d394ac63110df4340e895aadd94a0b116000e2","tid":2095044,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b3fcc086a8c148fd04e1e0007fc32f281ee470","tid":2095044,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7d394ac63110df4340e895aadd94a0b116000e2","tid":2095044